<h1 id="lab-managing-python-dependencies--virtual-environments">Lab:
Managing Python Dependencies &amp; Virtual Environments</h1>
<h2 id="objectives">Objectives</h2>
<ul>
<li>Understand the importance of managing Python dependencies.</li>
<li>Learn how to create and use virtual environments.</li>
<li>Explore different methods for specifying project dependencies.</li>
<li>Practice installing and verifying dependencies in an isolated
environment.</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="real-world-scenario">Real-World Scenario</h2>
<p>Imagine you are developing a data analysis tool for your team. Each
project may require different versions of libraries like
<code>requests</code> and <code>numpy</code>. To avoid conflicts and
ensure reproducibility, you need to isolate your project's dependencies
using a virtual environment and document them for easy setup by other
team members.</p>
<h2 id="step-1-create-a-virtual-environment">Step 1: Create a Virtual
Environment</h2>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb1"><pre
class="sourceCode bash"><code class="sourceCode bash"><span id="cb1-1"><a href="#cb1-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="ex">python</span> <span class="at">-m</span> venv venv</span></code></pre></div>
<p>Activate the environment:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Windows:</strong></li>
</ul>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb2"><pre
class="sourceCode bash"><code class="sourceCode bash"><span id="cb2-1"><a href="#cb2-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="ex">venv\Scripts\activate</span></span></code></pre></div>
<ul>
<li><strong>macOS/Linux:</strong></li>
</ul>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb3"><pre
class="sourceCode bash"><code class="sourceCode bash"><span id="cb3-1"><a href="#cb3-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="bu">source</span> venv/bin/activate</span></code></pre></div>
<h2 id="step-2-define-dependencies">Step 2: Define Dependencies</h2>
<h3
id="option-1-using-pyprojecttoml-recommended-for-modern-projects">Option
1: Using <code>pyproject.toml</code> (Recommended for modern
projects)</h3>
<ol type="1">
<li>Create a <code>pyproject.toml</code> file:</li>
</ol>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb4"><pre
class="sourceCode toml"><code class="sourceCode toml"><span id="cb4-1"><a href="#cb4-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="kw">[project]</span></span>
<span id="cb4-2"><a href="#cb4-2" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="dt">name</span> <span class="op">=</span> <span class="st">&quot;retail-insights&quot;</span></span>
<span id="cb4-3"><a href="#cb4-3" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="dt">version</span> <span class="op">=</span> <span class="st">&quot;0.1.0&quot;</span></span>
<span id="cb4-4"><a href="#cb4-4" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="dt">dependencies</span> <span class="op">=</span> <span class="op">[</span></span>
<span id="cb4-5"><a href="#cb4-5" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>    <span class="st">&quot;numpy&gt;=2.3.5&quot;</span><span class="op">,</span></span>
<span id="cb4-6"><a href="#cb4-6" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>    <span class="st">&quot;pandas&gt;=2.3.3&quot;</span></span>
<span id="cb4-7"><a href="#cb4-7" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="op">]</span></span></code></pre></div>
<ol start="2" type="1">
<li>Install dependencies (using <a
href="https://pip.pypa.io/en/stable/">pip</a> or <a
href="https://pdm.fming.dev/">pdm</a>):</li>
</ol>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb5"><pre
class="sourceCode bash"><code class="sourceCode bash"><span id="cb5-1"><a href="#cb5-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="ex">pip</span> install requests numpy</span></code></pre></div>
<h3 id="option-2-using-requirementstxt">Option 2: Using
<code>requirements.txt</code></h3>
<ol type="1">
<li>Create a <code>requirements.txt</code> file:</li>
</ol>
<pre class="plaintext"><code>requests==2.31.0
numpy==1.26.0</code></pre>
<ol start="2" type="1">
<li>Install dependencies:</li>
</ol>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb7"><pre
class="sourceCode bash"><code class="sourceCode bash"><span id="cb7-1"><a href="#cb7-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="ex">pip</span> install <span class="at">-r</span> requirements.txt</span></code></pre></div>
<h3 id="option-3-using-setuppy-for-packaging">Option 3: Using
<code>setup.py</code> (for packaging)</h3>
<ol type="1">
<li>Create a <code>setup.py</code> file:</li>
</ol>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb8"><pre
class="sourceCode python"><code class="sourceCode python"><span id="cb8-1"><a href="#cb8-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="im">from</span> setuptools <span class="im">import</span> setup</span>
<span id="cb8-2"><a href="#cb8-2" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a></span>
<span id="cb8-3"><a href="#cb8-3" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>setup(</span>
<span id="cb8-4"><a href="#cb8-4" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>        name<span class="op">=</span><span class="st">&quot;lab04-example&quot;</span>,</span>
<span id="cb8-5"><a href="#cb8-5" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>        version<span class="op">=</span><span class="st">&quot;0.1.0&quot;</span>,</span>
<span id="cb8-6"><a href="#cb8-6" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>        install_requires<span class="op">=</span>[</span>
<span id="cb8-7"><a href="#cb8-7" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>                <span class="st">&quot;requests==2.31.0&quot;</span>,</span>
<span id="cb8-8"><a href="#cb8-8" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>                <span class="st">&quot;numpy==1.26.0&quot;</span></span>
<span id="cb8-9"><a href="#cb8-9" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>        ]</span>
<span id="cb8-10"><a href="#cb8-10" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>)</span></code></pre></div>
<ol start="2" type="1">
<li>Install dependencies:</li>
</ol>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb9"><pre
class="sourceCode bash"><code class="sourceCode bash"><span id="cb9-1"><a href="#cb9-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="ex">pip</span> install .</span></code></pre></div>
<h2 id="step-3-verify-installation">Step 3: Verify Installation</h2>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb10"><pre
class="sourceCode python"><code class="sourceCode python"><span id="cb10-1"><a href="#cb10-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="im">import</span> requests</span>
<span id="cb10-2"><a href="#cb10-2" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="im">import</span> numpy</span>
<span id="cb10-3"><a href="#cb10-3" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a></span>
<span id="cb10-4"><a href="#cb10-4" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="bu">print</span>(requests.__version__)</span>
<span id="cb10-5"><a href="#cb10-5" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="bu">print</span>(numpy.__version__)</span></code></pre></div>
<h2 id="step-4-deactivate-the-virtual-environment">Step 4: Deactivate
the Virtual Environment</h2>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb11"><pre
class="sourceCode bash"><code class="sourceCode bash"><span id="cb11-1"><a href="#cb11-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="ex">deactivate</span></span></code></pre></div>
